---
// About section — SPEC-design-v1
---

<section class="about">
  <div class="inner">

    <div class="photo-col">
      <img
        class="photo"
        src="/assets/cases/ure/photo.png"
        alt="Igor Bielov"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="text-col">
      <p class="label">About</p>
      <p class="body">
        Hi, I'm Igor — a product designer with 7+ years
        of experience, working remotely. I care about the
        whole picture: not just whether something is usable,
        but whether it makes sense for the business behind it.
        That means thinking about how users first encounter
        a product, what keeps them coming back, and what makes
        the business viable enough to keep improving it.
        A product that works for users and for the people
        building it is always the goal.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 160px auto 160px;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 64px;
    width: 824px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ─── Photo ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .photo-col {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-surface);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .photo {
    display: block;
    width: 280px;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ─── Text ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .text-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 480px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .body {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about {
      padding: 0 20px;
      margin: 120px auto 120px;
    }

    .inner {
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .photo {
      width: 120px;
    }
  }
</style>
